---
description: Unrecorded project rules
globs:
  - "**/*.dart"
  - "**/*.kt"
  - "**/*.swift"
  - "**/*.yaml"
  - "**/*.md"
alwaysApply: true
---

Follow the project guidance in `AGENTS.md`.

Keep edits small, testable, and privacy-first.

Do not add analytics, cloud services, ad SDKs, accounts, telemetry, ML detection, or extra AI configuration files unless explicitly requested.

When changing detection, scoring, permissions, or privacy-sensitive behaviour, update the relevant tests and concise docs.

Unrecorded must never claim to prove someone is recording. It only alerts users to possible nearby recording risk.
